The paper deals with matching markets, which is a topic in game theory (cs.GT). It also involves coalition formation games, which is a subfield of AI (cs.AI). The use of constraints and the study of dynamics suggest that it may also be relevant to social networks and complex systems (cs.SI). The paper also involves the analysis of algorithms and computational complexity, which falls under the category of data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) and machine learning (cs.LG).
